'''酞嗪'''（英語：Phthalazine）是一种杂环化合物，化学式C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>6</sub>N<sub>2</sub>，由一个[[苯环|苯环]]与一个[[哒嗪|哒嗪]]环稠合而成。喹唑啉也可看做[[萘|萘]]环的两个CH被N原子替换，这样的结构称为[[萘啶|萘啶]]。酞嗪及其衍生物不存在于自然界。<ref name="Raymond N. Castle"> {{cite | author = Raymond N. Castle | title = The Chemistry of Heterocyclic Compounds, Condensed Pyridazines Including ... | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | ISBN 047018848-0 = | year = 2009 <!--| Online = {{Google Book | BuchID lQx33bsWwdMC = | page = 324}} -->| pages = 324ff}} </ref>

==合成==
1,2-二(二溴甲基)苯与[[肼|肼]]缩合，或用磷和氢碘酸还原氯酞嗪合成。
==应用==
酞嗪被用作有机合成的起始原料。<ref name="Desmond J. Brown, Jonathan A. Ellman, Edward C. Taylor"> {{cite journal | author = Desmond J. Brown, Jonathan A. Ellman, Edward C. Taylor | title = Cinnolines and Phthalazines: Chemistry of Heterocyclic Compounds, Supplement II | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | ISBN 047174411-5 = | year = 2005 | page = 175}}</ref>
